title: Horrible platform full of glitches, every shipment has issues
reviews: Every time I create a shipment I need to call you guys at least 3times. You have the worst platform imaginable. No matter how many timesI complain it never gets fixed. Every time a new unpleasant surprise. Just an example: two days ago I created a shipment US to UK. I scheduled the pickup for the next morning. FedEx never came by. I called today and talked directly to someone at FirstChoice. She said sorry and scheduled a newFedEx pickup reassuring me that it will get picked up today. I hung up the phone and 2 minutes later I get a call from FedEx that the pick up scheduled was completely missing the address. It only had the city of Wellington, CO. How in the world do you guys function and retain customers???

title: Although I have been using First Choice since the start of my company....
reviews:
1. Surprised by the Japan Customs stoppage and subsequent paperwork and delay in shipping.
2. Lack of response on VAT or GST invoices for shipments to Canada and Japan. I have asked several times and still do not have resolution. This is a must have to continue doing business.
3. Difficulty in getting invoice details (VAT charges vs. Shipping related charges) aligned with payments. It takes me manually looking at three reports from you website to get this information. Required for Financial accounting.
